Usage Recommendations:

For Header/Navigation:

Background: #2d2d2d (dark-primary)
Text: #fce303 (primary-yellow)
Hover states: #fee749 (yellow-light)


For Main Content:

Background: #ffffff (white)
Text: #2d2d2d (dark-primary)
Headings: #424242 (dark-secondary)


For Buttons:

Primary Button: #fce303 with #2d2d2d text
Secondary Button: #2d2d2d with #ffffff text
Hover States: #fee749 (yellow-light)


For Sections:

Alternating sections: #f5f5f5 (gray-light)
Feature boxes: #e0e0e0 (gray-medium)


For Accents:

Links: #037ffc (accent-blue)
Special highlights: #7b03fc (accent-purple)